data.description: Welcome to your dream home with a stunning lake view from the property! This like new, 5 bedroom, 3 bath home sits at the end of a quiet cul de sac on a large lot in a beautiful wooded setting at Doe Valley. The open-concept layout integrates kitchen, dining, and living space with 10 foot ceilings.  The kitchen features quartz countertops, custom tile backsplash, a farmhouse style sink, and a large pantry.  On the main level, 3 bedrooms are arranged in a split floorplan with the large primary suite on one side and the remaining two bedrooms and bath on the other.  The primary suite has a separate shower and tub and a walk in closet with access to the laundry room from the closet as well as from the foyer off the kitchen and garage.  The fourth and fifth bedrooms are in the newly finished walk-out basement that boasts 8 1/2 ft ceilings along with a full bath, living room, and ample storage space.  There are covered back decks on both levels of the home overlooking the beautiful, wooded backyard.  This home also has an assumable VA loan at 3% interest.
